  <brief_title>The Effects of Topical Calcium Glycerophosphate on Surgical Wound Healing and Residual Scarring</brief_title>
  <acronym>TOPCGP-2008</acronym>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Single Blind, Comparative, Controlled Study On The Effects Of Topical Calcium Glycerophosphate On Surgical Wound Healing And Residual Scarring In Bilateral Total Knee Arthroplasty Patients</official_title>
